msgid "Twi'leks are a species from the planet Ryloth known for their prehensile tentacles (also known as lekku) and a diverse range of skin pigments. While some see the species as nothing more than a commodity, untold more understand them to be hardened and relentless freedom fighters.¬¬During the rise of the First Order, numerous Twi'leks feared an occupation of their homeworld would be inevitable. While Ryloth was officially an independent planet, many swore allegiance to General Leia Organa and the Resistance."
